from scipy.stats import pearsonr
In [4]:
# 计算Pearson相关系数和P值
def pearson_corr_matrix(df):
    corr_matrix = df.corr(method='pearson')
    p_values = pd.DataFrame(np.zeros(corr_matrix.shape), columns=df.columns, index=df.columns)
    
    for row in df.columns:
        for col in df.columns:
            _, p = pearsonr(df[row], df[col])
            p_values.loc[row, col] = p
    
    return corr_matrix, p_values

In [9]:
corrs = corr_matrix
p = p_values

# 创建遮罩：保留下三角（不含对角线）
mask = np.tril(np.ones_like(corrs, dtype=bool), k=-1)

annot_data = np.where(
    (p < 0.05),  # 只标注下三角中 p < 0.05 的地方
    np.vectorize(lambda x: f'{x:.2f}')(corrs),
    ""
)

# 创建主图
plt.figure(figsize=(6, 5), facecolor='white', dpi=600)
ax = plt.gca()  # 获取当前主坐标轴
# 绘制热力图
sns.heatmap(
    corrs,
    mask=mask,
    annot=annot_data,
    linewidth=0.5,
    vmin=-1, vmax=1,
    square=True,
    cmap='coolwarm',
    fmt="",
    annot_kws={"size": 10, "color": 'k'},
    cbar_kws={
#         'label': 'Correlation Coefficient',
        'ticks': [-1, -0.5, 0, 0.5, 1],
        "pad": 0.2,
        "shrink": 0.9
    },
    ax=ax
)

# 设置坐标标签
ax.set_xticks(np.arange(n) + .5)
ax.set_xticklabels(labels, rotation=45, ha="left", rotation_mode="anchor")

ax.set_yticks(np.arange(n) + .5)
ax.set_yticklabels(labels, rotation=0)

# 调整坐标轴显示位置
ax.tick_params(
    top=True, bottom=False, left=False, right=True,
    labeltop=True, labelbottom=False,
    labelleft=False, labelright=True
)

# 去除边框
for spine in ax.spines.values():
    spine.set_visible(False)

# 设置标题
# ax.set_title('相关性热力图（仅下三角）', fontsize=16, loc='left')

# colorbar 样式
cbar = ax.collections[0].colorbar
cbar.ax.yaxis.label.set_size(10)
cbar.ax.tick_params(labelsize=9)

# 显示图像
plt.tight_layout()
# plt.savefig("G://University//GradePrediction//processwork//figure//figure 05 a.png", dpi=600, bbox_inches='tight', transparent=False)
plt.show()
